            SECTION 1: OVERVIEW
            
            Your privacy and the security of your personal information are very important to us. We want you to be as comfortable as possible visiting our Website and ordering our food products.

            This Privacy Policy explains how we collect your personal information, how we protect your personal information, and the choices you have concerning the use of such information.

